source.name: Annual Summary Electricity Statistics for the U. S.
source.description: Contains annual data back to 1998 at the national level for electricity generation; capacity; consumption and cost of fossil fuels; sales, price and revenue; emissions; demand-side management; and operating revenues, expenses, and income
